title: Thickening haze in Singapore disrupts World Cup swim races
text:
> Sports Thickening haze in Singapore disrupts World Cup swim races The financial skyline is seen through a thick haze, Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015, in Singapore. The haze is caused by the burning of forests in Indonesia's Sumatra and Borneo islands. (AP Photo/Wong Maye-E)
